{"tid":1950692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「石斑」及「鮑魚」食品樣本與聲稱不符　7名男女被捕","createTime":"2020-03-30T13:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T13:41:44.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6912e058603fd5a1c0ae5878aefbc5aa1dad4c8e","tid":1950692,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"海關從多間食肆試購「石斑」及「鮑魚」等食品化驗，發現14個聲稱「石斑」及6個聲稱「鮑魚」的食品，化驗結果分別是鯰魚及魷魚，與聲稱不符，拘捕7名男女，年齡介乎47歲至62歲，包括涉案食肆的5名董事及2名東主。<br />\n<br />\n海關上星期在全港多區採取針對食肆供應附有虛假商品說明食的品行動，其中7間分別位於上水、大埔、葵涌、油麻地、土瓜灣、灣仔及鰂魚涌的食肆，出售的貨品與聲稱不同，案件仍在調查。<br />\n<br />\n海關提醒商戶要遵守《條例》的規定，消費者購買商品時應光顧信譽良好的商戶。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天使蛋糕無天使咬左美心未?</span>"},{"pid":"56a4ab6f18fefebfb78afa558f02380eebff696f","tid":1950692,"uid":81273,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:05:49.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faeb3e28fab1860aa7622d4022098749dd02103","tid":1950692,"uid":51469,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"冇呀,<br />\n因為人地冇你咁冇腦兼弱智呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13faf49c1547992b72af957754d65b4067027d08","tid":1950692,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"有兩隻五毛入黎"},{"pid":"14d3701060ffceb64a62af33c58c25e611c91128","tid":1950692,"uid":66697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"舉報啦，無撚聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729fafaebda18fd6d3cbf4eb452f78642f65c9aa","tid":1950692,"uid":182615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:08:48.000Z","msg":"斑喃冇石斑"},{"pid":"0837ecca56bc0f8bfbc25353f58987a0f94abf30","tid":1950692,"uid":200663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30